{"tid":1555830,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有半個鐘！！！","createTime":"2019-09-09T13:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T17:00:45.000Z","uid":174882,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"97fd7b11a54186e6d35da9d15e382ca8e5bf1711","tid":1555830,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"我哋就要鳩叫！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但嗌前要播一次願榮光歸香港<br />\n每晚都要播一次！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整喊大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:點播？<br />\nA:大家屋企有咩喇叭拎曬出嚟  對住窗外播<br />\n<br />\nQ:驚好亂唔同步？<br />\nA:去google play/app store下載&quot;amp me&quot;，我會開個room俾大家入嚟同步播放<br />\n<br />\nQ:如果俾五毛/廢老屌嘈住佢點算？<br />\nA:再播大聲啲！<br />\n<br />\nQ:可唔可以跟住唱？<br />\nA:梗係可以啦！唔跟住唱點樣快啲緊記歌詞？<br />\n<br />\nQ:點解要咁做？<br />\nA:因為我連續嗌兩晚，聲都沙晒，唔可長久嗌落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>播完之後歡迎繼續嗌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ca774a8250edb6973153da1261a54cb29d4b6462","tid":1555830,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"傳送門：<a href=\"https://ampme.com/party/1568035540569/HK4Gke3sGm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fampme.com%2Fparty%2F1568035540569%2FHK4Gke3sGm&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BuuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d76dd020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ampme.com/party/1568035540569/HK4Gke3sGm</a>"},{"pid":"f94728b58dde3715b54ab6f3ce3ae4744280674d","tid":1555830,"uid":174882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"記住綁實個喇叭  唔好跌咗落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966705699285cfd8120a714d1b30f334c0658fd8","tid":1555830,"uid":29979,"like":0,